Frameworks:
- standards for how to secure facilities
- ISA 62443 - Gold Standard for OT/ICS cybersecurity (Cost money)
  -a little hard to read
- ISA (American) IEC (International)
- OT cybersecurity NIST SP 800-82r3 (Free)
  -simpler writing
- Environments decide on what their level of security should be
  -are we protecting against error to are we protecting against state actors

